I uploaded my PMK Hijikata Fanart in Photos.
Yes, he actually has some red eyeliner...actually you can blame the
crayola markers I purchased...the felt tip screwed up everything so I
used a bit of red to cover up something and thought "heck" heroes in
Japanese prints have red around the eyes.  The drawing was done on
paper taped together (you'll see a thin white line near the bottom.  I
submitted this fanart to the contest.
